OMNET++ Modules for Blockchain Network Simulation

Components
==========

FullNode (FullNode.ned, FullNode.cc)
  Blockchain node capable of mining and forwarding blocks.

ethp2p (ethp2p.msg)
  P2P messages loosely based on Ethereum devp2p.

scripts/randreg.py
  Generate random regular graphs.

Build
=====

opp_makemake -f
make

Misc
====

Logging in command line interface

  To enable logging in command line, set
      cmdenv-express-mode = false
  in omnetpp.ini.
